cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.DL, cs.DB 

Reasoning: 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is the most likely category as the paper discusses information search systems and search modes. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also likely as the paper proposes new interaction paradigms to guide users in their searches. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper deals with textual corpus and semantic visualization. 
- cs.DL (Digital Libraries) is relevant as the paper discusses navigation in textual corpus. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper proposes a semantic approach to information search and navigation.
